<item>
            <title>[SPR-965] MethodInvokingFactoryBean does not support autowiring</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-965</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Consider the following example, where System.err is redefined using &lt;br/&gt;
MethodInvokingFactoryBean.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;beans&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;bean id=&quot;err&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
        class=&quot;java.io.File&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;constructor-arg&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;value&amp;gt;c:/err1.txt&amp;lt;/value&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;/constructor-arg&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/bean&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &amp;lt;bean id=&quot;ok&quot; class=&quot;org.springframework.beans.factory.config.MethodInvokingFactoryBean&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;property name=&quot;staticMethod&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;value&amp;gt;java.lang.System.setErr&amp;lt;/value&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;/property&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;property name=&quot;arguments&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;bean class=&quot;java.io.PrintStream&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;constructor-arg&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                    &amp;lt;ref local=&quot;err&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;/constructor-arg&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;/bean&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;/property&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/bean&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/beans&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Create an Application context and write in System.err:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;ApplicationContext bf =&lt;br/&gt;
   new ClassPathXmlApplicationContext(myConfFile);&lt;br/&gt;
System.err.println(&quot;Hello&quot;);&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It works just fine.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Now consider this second example, where the PrintStream is autowired:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;beans&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;bean id=&quot;err&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
        class=&quot;java.io.File&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;constructor-arg&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;value&amp;gt;c:/err2.txt&amp;lt;/value&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;/constructor-arg&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/bean&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &amp;lt;bean id=&quot;bad&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
        class=&quot;org.springframework.beans.factory.config.MethodInvokingFactoryBean&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;property name=&quot;staticMethod&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;value&amp;gt;java.lang.System.setErr&amp;lt;/value&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;/property&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;property name=&quot;arguments&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;bean class=&quot;java.io.PrintStream&quot; autowire=&quot;autodetect&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;/property&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/bean&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/beans&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Spring throws a NullPointerException:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;at org.springframework.beans.factory.config.MethodInvokingFactoryBean.getObjectType(MethodInvokingFactoryBean.java:126)&lt;br/&gt;
at org.springframework.beans.factory.support.AbstractBeanFactory.getType(AbstractBeanFactory.java:348)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Looks like Spring, while trying to find a matching bean, calls getObjectType() in MethodInvokingFactoryBean before it is prepare()d.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
